We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

snippet.title: MUTTON BIRYANI | 3 FULL GOAT ROASTED MUTTON BIRYANI Recipe Cooking in Village | Arabian Biryani
snippet.description: Today in our village, we cooked a grand Arabian-style mutton biryani using three full goats. First, we boiled the whole goats in a large vessel with spices to make the meat tender and flavorful. Then, we carefully roasted each goat on a large tawa over a direct flame of firewood, adding a smoky, rich layer of flavor. After roasting, we layered the juicy mutton with aromatic basmati rice, hand-ground masalas, and traditional spices. This massive biryani was slow-cooked to perfection and shared during a village feast. A perfect blend of smoky, spicy, and tender mutton biryani with an Arabian touch.

id.description: Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak biryani daging kambing ala Arab yang megah menggunakan tiga ekor kambing utuh. Sung and composed by Darshan himself, with heartfelt lyrics by Siddharth A. Bhavsar and Darshan Raval, the song captures the innocence of two hearts setting out on a beautiful, unknown journey of love. snippet.title: Alice in Borderland: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice in Borderland: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

As new deadly games return, Arisu, Usagi and new players must navigate even more daunting, adrenaline-fueled challenges.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

snippet.title: What Real Growth Means ‚Äì Girish Mathrubootham, Founder & Executive Chairman, Freshworks | Gobinath
snippet.description:
Enquiries:
talk2gobinath@gmail.com

#Gobinath #girishmathrubootham #freshworks #startup #india #podcast #saas #ai #artificialintelligence #business #thegobinathpodcast #careeradvice #techleadership 

Stay ahead with direct updates from Gobinath ‚Äî interviews, insights, and powerful voices.
Join the official WhatsApp Channel today:
https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Vb5gNn82Jl8DSfwhUM3G

     ‚ÄúSaaS is Dead. AI is the New King.‚Äù
In this high-impact episode, Gobinath sits down with Girish Mathrubootham, one of India‚Äôs most admired tech leaders, to explore the rise of AI, the future of startups, and what it takes to stay relevant in a world that‚Äôs changing faster than ever.

From the early days of Freshworks to launching Freddy AI, from the AI disruption wave to solving real customer problems ‚Äî Girish opens up like never before. He talks about career lessons, handling challenges, building for Gen Z, and why he believes India is ready to lead the AI era.

üîç Topics Covered in This Episode:
 ‚Ä¢ Freshworks and Riding the Wave
 ‚Ä¢ The Rise of AI ‚Äì A Monster Wave
 ‚Ä¢ Adapting Freshworks to the AI Era
 ‚Ä¢ Why AI Is a Disruptive Monster
 ‚Ä¢ Is SaaS Dead? The Shift to AI with Freddy
 ‚Ä¢ How AI Enhances SaaS
 ‚Ä¢ Layoffs & AI‚Äôs Human Impact
 ‚Ä¢ India‚Äôs Transition: Services to Products
 ‚Ä¢ The Real Product Revolution
 ‚Ä¢ Why India‚Äôs Moment is Now
 ‚Ä¢ Moving to the US & Evolving Indian Mindsets
 ‚Ä¢ Can Indian Startups Match Global Valuations?
 ‚Ä¢ Girish Presents All In to Superstar Rajinikanth
 ‚Ä¢ How Local Wisdom Shaped a Global Founder
 ‚Ä¢ Gut Feeling, Luck & Success ‚Äì Girish‚Äôs Philosophy
 ‚Ä¢ Parallels with Dhoni‚Äôs CSK Leadership
 ‚Ä¢ Career = Tripod: Knowledge, Challenge & Salary

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Blessed With Baby Boy Allhamdullilahüë∂üèª‚ù§Ô∏è | Adnaan 07
snippet.description:
Today, my life changed forever.
I became a father and Alhamdulillah, it‚Äôs a baby boy.

The moment I heard his first cry, something inside me shifted. A love I never knew existed was born. It‚Äôs hard to put into words what it feels like, but I tried capturing every moment, every emotion, and every heartbeat.

This video holds one of the most precious memories of my life. The arrival of my son. The nervousness, the joy, the tears, and the silent prayers.

Thank you for being a part of this journey. Your love and duas mean more than words can ever say.

This is the beginning of something truly beautiful. Do remember us in your prayers.‚ú®

#FathersLove #BabyBoy #Adnaan07 #AdnaanShaikh

snippet.title: Renault Dacia Duster 2025 Drive Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste. If the Ford Endeavour is the most anticipated SUV Indians are waiting for, it is the Duster that Renault fans are waiting for. Fortunately, the French have not left India like the Americans did, so we can say that Duster will come before Endeavour if the Almighty listens to our prayers. Here is a walkaround and drive Impression of the all-new Duster, which is already on sale in many markets outside India. 


Timestamps:
00:00 Introduction
01:29 Exteriors including Key fob, Wheels, Doors, Boot, Headlights, ADAS, etc
09:00 Engine Bay
09:40 Interiors including MID, Infotainment, Seats, Space etc
23:08 Rear seat Space and Amenities
25:05 Drive Impressions Including Ride, Handling, Engine, Gearbox, braking and Fuel Economy
33:56 Conclusion
